  descriptions:
  - 'Chronosant is the Imperial capital of the Intergalactic Empire. '
  - 'The Intergalactic Empire was founded 30,000 years ago during the conquest of
    Samaron the Conquerer. '
  - 'For the majority of the time since then, the Intergalactic empire kept the peace
    and ensured free trade across the various galaxies they control. '
  - The Intergalactic Empire is one of the main reasons for the spread of the ArrowHex
    game across the universe as it ensured trade and collaboration across the Empire.
